  - m_Id: 864226270015
    m_Localized: Vehicle Assembly Plant
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270101
    m_Localized: A chemical processing facility that transforms crude oil into fabric
      and other synthetic materials. Produces fabric from oil, enabling textile production
      without relying solely on wood.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270102
    m_Localized: A precision manufacturing facility for producing mechanical components,
      electronic components, and precision tools. Produces machine parts, electronic
      components, and precision tools from refined metals. Essential for advanced
      production chains.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270103
    m_Localized: A specialized facility for manufacturing high-performance internal
      combustion engines. Produces engines from machine parts, electronic components,
      and steel ingots. Essential prerequisite for vehicle production.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270104
    m_Localized: A heavy industry facility specializing in precision tools and luxury
      goods. Produces precision tools and premium products from high-grade steel
      and advanced components. Requires significant investment but yields high-value
      products.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270105
    m_Localized: A versatile light industry facility that produces consumer goods
      including furniture, clothing, and simple tools. Flexible production allows
      switching between different product lines based on market demand.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270106
    m_Localized: A loading station where resources are picked up from storage and
      loaded onto the production line. Workers efficiently transfer materials to
      begin the manufacturing process.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270116
    m_Localized: A logging camp that harvests raw timber from nearby forests. Produces
      logs without consuming any auxiliary materials. First step in the wood production
      chain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270108
    m_Localized: A military-grade manufacturing facility for producing weapons and
      munitions. Produces small arms, heavy arms, and munitions from steel ingots
      and machine parts. Essential for wartime production with high demand during
      conflicts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270109
    m_Localized: A deep-shaft mining facility that extracts iron ore, coal, copper
      ore, gold ore, and aluminum ore from the earth. Requires significant investment
      but provides essential raw materials for industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270110
    m_Localized: An oil drilling facility that extracts crude oil from underground
      reserves. Essential for fuel production and chemical processing. Requires high
      maintenance costs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270111
    m_Localized: A transportation pathway that connects different areas of the production
      line. Essential infrastructure for moving resources and products efficiently
      between facilities.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270112
    m_Localized: A logging camp that harvests raw timber from nearby forests. Produces
      logs without consuming any auxiliary materials. First step in the wood production
      chain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270113
    m_Localized: A smelting facility that transforms raw ores into refined metal
      ingots. Processes iron ore, copper ore, aluminum ore, and gold ore into their
      respective ingots. Essential for metalworking industries.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270114
    m_Localized: An unloading station where finished products are removed from the
      production line and stored. Workers carefully handle completed items for inventory
      management.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270115
    m_Localized: A massive industrial facility for assembling vehicles. Requires
      extensive components, electronics, and materials to produce cars, airplanes,
      and tanks.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270201
    m_Localized: Distribution
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270202
    m_Localized: Production
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22446163628539904
    m_Localized: Raw Production
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270016
    m_Localized: Splitter
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270117
    m_Localized: Splits incoming resources into two lanes. At base rotation it alternates output to the right and downward lanes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270017
    m_Localized: Tunnel
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270118
    m_Localized: A two-lane pass-through road. Vertical and horizontal traffic are buffered separately and move without blocking each other.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270018
    m_Localized: Gold Mine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 864226270119
    m_Localized: A dedicated mining facility that targets rich gold-bearing ore bodies. Extracts gold ore for refining and downstream manufacturing.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
